<div class="policy-page full-width">
  <div class="policy-page-inner">
    <h1 class="policy-page-title">{{ page.title }}</h1>
    <div class="policy-page-content">
      {% if page.content != blank %}
        {{ page.content }}
      {% else %}
        <p>We strive to dispatch your order promptly, subject to product availability and credit verification. Please note that delivery estimates are approximate and may occasionally extend, particularly during peak holiday seasons.</p>

        <table class="shipping-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Location</th>
              <th>Order Value</th>
              <th>Shipping Fee</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Australia</td>
              <td>Over AUD$150</td>
              <td>Free</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Australia</td>
              <td>Under AUD$150</td>
              <td>AUD$18.95</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>New Zealand</td>
              <td>Over AUD$250</td>
              <td>Free</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>New Zealand</td>
              <td>Under AUD$250</td>
              <td>AUD$25.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Other Countries</td>
              <td>Any</td>
              <td>Varies by Country</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>Order Processing Time</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Processed within 3-5 business days.</li>
          <li><strong>Express:</strong> Processed within 1-3 business days.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Note: Business days exclude Weekends and Australian public holidays.</em></p>

        <h2>Partial Shipping</h2>
        <p>If your order contains a combination of items available for immediate shipment and pre-order items, we will dispatch the entire order once all items are in stock. Should you wish to receive the in-stock items separately, we recommend placing separate orders.</p>

        <h2>TRACKING</h2>
        <p>You should have received an email confirming your order when you completed the checkout process. Please check your junk/spam folder if you cannot find it. If you haven't received the order confirmation email, please contact <a href="mailto:houseofbrandssupport@gmail.com">houseofbrandssupport@gmail.com</a>. Once the order has been dispatched, you will receive a shipping confirmation email containing your Tracking ID. Enter the ID on courier website to stay informed about all movements of your parcels.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .policy-page { background: #fff; min-height: 60vh; }
  .policy-page-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 40px 80px; }
  .policy-page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-base); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 40px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }
  .policy-page-content { font-family: var(--font-base); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; }
  .policy-page-content h2, .policy-page-content h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin: 30px 0 15px; color: #111; }
  .policy-page-content p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .policy-page-content a { color: #111; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }

  /* Shipping Table */
  .shipping-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-family: var(--font-base);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .shipping-table th {
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .shipping-table td {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    color: #333;
  }
  .shipping-table tbody tr:hover {
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-page-inner { padding: 100px 20px 60px; }
    .policy-page-title { font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .shipping-table th, .shipping-table td { padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 13px; }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping Form",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Shipping Form" }]
}
{% endschema %}
